            . I am an officer. I took the prisoner, and received this spoon from the butler.</p>
               <p>(Property produced and sworn to.)</p>
               <p>The prisoner put in a written Defence; stating, that he had called at the house to inquire for a situation, and denied having had the spoon in his possession.</p>
